 ARRAY['SuccessBLOC pre-built programmes reduce CS implementation time from months to days', 'Modular architecture lets teams activate specific programmes without full platform configuration', 'Free plan available for early-stage CS teams with limited account volumes', 'AI flags early churn signals before accounts become urgent risk cases'],
 ARRAY['SuccessBLOC library is most valuable for standard SaaS use cases - complex custom models require more configuration', 'Reporting depth is less advanced than Gainsight for enterprise analytics requirements', 'Health score customisation requires understanding of the weighting system'],
