('churnzero',
 'ChurnZero',
 'Real-time customer success platform for SaaS companies focused on reducing churn and increasing net revenue retention',
 'ChurnZero is a customer success platform built specifically for subscription SaaS businesses, with a focus on real-time signals and immediate action. The platform aggregates product usage data, support activity, NPS responses, and CRM information to build dynamic customer health scores that update continuously as customer behaviour changes - not just nightly or weekly. This real-time approach means CS managers receive alerts when a customer''s engagement drops sharply, when a power user goes inactive, or when a support spike suggests a problem, enabling intervention while there is still time to turn the account around. ChurnZero Journeys automates personalised touchpoints across the customer lifecycle - welcome sequences, feature adoption nudges, renewal communications, and win-back campaigns - triggered by customer behaviour rather than fixed calendar dates. The in-app notification system lets CS and product teams push contextual messages, surveys, and feature announcements directly within the customer''s product session. ChurnZero AI analyses churn risk across the customer base and provides predictive scores and recommended interventions. The platform integrates with Salesforce, Hubspot, Zendesk, Intercom, and major billing systems including Stripe and Chargebee. Used by mid-market and growth-stage SaaS companies including Shutterstock, Netsol, and Recurly to systematically improve net revenue retention across their customer base.',
