('planhat',
 'Planhat',
 'Modern customer success platform combining health scoring, revenue analytics, and team collaboration',
 'Planhat is a customer success platform designed for modern SaaS CS teams, combining customer health management, revenue analytics, task management, and team playbooks in a clean, intuitive interface that requires less configuration overhead than traditional CS enterprise platforms. The platform ingests data from CRM, billing, product analytics, and support systems to build a multi-dimensional view of each customer account - usage trends, contract value, expansion potential, support health, and engagement with the CS team. Planhat''s revenue analytics layer makes it the tool of choice for CS teams with clear ownership of net revenue retention - the platform tracks expansion MRR, contraction, and churn contribution by CS manager, segment, and cohort, connecting CS activity to the revenue metrics that matter to the business. Collaboration features including shared timelines, internal notes, and stakeholder relationship maps enable cross-functional coordination on strategic accounts without relying on email chains. Planhat AI suggests optimal outreach timing and next best actions based on each customer''s engagement pattern. The platform integrates with Salesforce, Hubspot, Stripe, Chargebee, Segment, and Mixpanel. Used by CS teams at Vend, Teamwork, and Factorial for clear visibility into how customer health connects to revenue outcomes, and for giving individual CS managers an intuitive daily workspace that surfaces the accounts needing attention.',
 NULL,
