('vitally',
 'Vitally',
 'Customer success platform built for fast-growing SaaS companies with powerful reporting and Salesforce-level customisation',
 'Vitally is a customer success platform built for growth-stage SaaS companies that need the power of enterprise CS tools without the implementation complexity and cost. The platform is notable for its reporting depth and customisation - CS teams can build custom dashboards, segment cohorts by any attribute, and create bespoke health score models without needing professional services support. Vitally ingests data from product analytics, CRM, billing, and support systems and allows teams to define their own health metric weightings and threshold triggers. The Docs feature within Vitally enables CS managers to create structured account plans, success plans, and QBR templates that live alongside customer data rather than in a separate document tool. Project management features track onboarding milestones, implementation tasks, and strategic initiatives within the account, giving both the CS team and the customer visibility into progress. Vitally AI analyses account data to surface expansion signals and churn indicators with plain-language explanations of what the signals indicate and what action to take. The platform integrates with Salesforce, Hubspot, Segment, Intercom, Zendesk, Mixpanel, and Stripe. Vitally is the platform of choice for growth-stage SaaS companies including Productboard, Delighted, and Benchling that want Gainsight-level functionality at a price and implementation speed appropriate for a scaling team.',
