('client-success',
 'ClientSuccess',
 'Mid-market customer success platform for managing client relationships, health scoring, and CS team performance',
 'ClientSuccess is a customer success platform designed for mid-market SaaS companies that need a complete CS system without enterprise complexity. The platform manages the full customer lifecycle from onboarding through renewal, with health scoring, automated task management, success plan tracking, and CS team performance reporting in a package that smaller CS teams can configure and operate independently. ClientSuccess SuccessScore aggregates product usage, support history, relationship engagement, and financial metrics into a composite health indicator for every account. The platform tracks relationship engagement at the contact level - logging every call, email, and meeting with customer stakeholders and flagging accounts where executive relationships have gone cold or where a champion has not been reached in a defined period. SuccessPlans within ClientSuccess provide a structured framework for collaborative goal-setting with customers, creating a shared view of what success looks like and tracking progress against milestones that both the CS team and the customer can see. The reporting suite shows CS team performance metrics - tasks completed, playbook adherence, NPS trends, and renewal forecast accuracy - giving CS leaders data to coach and manage team performance. ClientSuccess integrates with Salesforce, Hubspot, Zendesk, and product analytics tools via native connectors and Zapier. Used by CS teams at companies including iQSTEL and Linksquares for client relationship management across a portfolio of accounts.',
