('custify',
 'Custify',
 'Customer success platform for B2B SaaS with automated lifecycle management and 360-degree health scoring',
 'Custify is a customer success platform designed for B2B SaaS companies that need a complete view of account health combined with automated lifecycle management. The platform aggregates customer data from CRM, product usage, billing, support, and email engagement into 360-degree health profiles for every account, giving CS managers a single screen view of everything happening in an account without switching between tools. Custify''s lifecycle automation engine triggers personalised customer interactions based on health events - a welcome sequence when a new customer is created, an adoption nudge when a key feature has not been used after two weeks, or an urgent intervention task when a health score drops below a defined threshold. The no-code automation builder lets CS teams configure these triggers and actions without technical support. Customer timelines within Custify log every interaction with an account - emails, calls, meetings, support tickets, and NPS responses - creating an auditable history that survives CS manager turnover. The reporting suite tracks NRR, churn rate, expansion MRR, and CS team activity metrics across the customer base with segmentation by plan, industry, or any custom attribute. Custify integrates with Stripe, Chargebee, Salesforce, Hubspot, Intercom, and Zendesk through native connectors. Used by B2B SaaS CS teams in Europe and internationally where a comprehensive CS platform is needed without the implementation complexity and cost of Gainsight.',
