('akita',
 'Akita',
 'Customer success platform for SaaS teams focused on data integration, health scoring, and account management',
 'Akita is a customer success platform that prioritises data integration flexibility and health score transparency, making it the choice for CS teams whose customer health is driven by complex, multi-source product usage data. The platform connects to an unusually wide range of data sources - product analytics tools, CRM, billing, support, email, and custom data via API - and lets CS teams define health score logic using any combination of these signals with full visibility into how each metric contributes to the overall score. Unlike opaque health scoring black boxes, Akita shows CS managers exactly why a score changed and which underlying metric drove the movement. Task management and playbook automation within Akita trigger CS activities based on health score thresholds, usage events, or calendar triggers. The platform includes customer-facing success plans that create a shared view of goals and milestones between the CS team and the customer. Account pulse reports provide a weekly digest of significant health changes across the portfolio, reducing the manual scanning required to identify which accounts need attention. Akita integrates with Stripe, Salesforce, Hubspot, Intercom, Zendesk, Amplitude, Mixpanel, Segment, and via Zapier for custom connections. Positioned for mid-market SaaS CS teams that need data integration depth and health score transparency above the level that simpler tools provide.',
